column5: Can someone confirm if Buffers Park boat launch is open  Thanks
By the looks of it you are Scarborough....
I am currently in Minden and deciding whether to take the boat down.

Well, ya didn't say that.  Anyway from F/B, is what I got. Bluffer's Park Marina They are, in the future please call 311 as they are the owners of the Toronto Public Launch and know the schedule better then us. Thank-you.  I just don't know how you would call 311 from up in the sticks.
